class="string">&quot;pause&quot;</span>);</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
